## ЁЯОи Icon Workflow (IMPORTANT!)

Since all apps share the same iOS folder, icons get overwritten. Always generate icons BEFORE building:

```bash
# USERAPP icons (green)
flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons:main -f flutter_launcher_icons_user.yaml

# ADMIN icons (green)
flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons:main -f flutter_launcher_icons_admin.yaml

# PARTNER icons (blue)
flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons:main -f flutter_launcher_icons_partner.yaml
```

**Rule:** Generate icons тЖТ Build тЖТ Archive (for each app separately)

---

## ЁЯЪА Build Commands

### USERAPP:
```bash
flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons:main -f flutter_launcher_icons_user.yaml
flutter build ios --release
# Bundle ID in Xcode: com.playmaker.app
```

### ADMIN:
```bash
flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons:main -f flutter_launcher_icons_admin.yaml
flutter build ios --release -t lib/main_admin.dart
# Bundle ID in Xcode: com.playmaker.admin
```

### PARTNER:
```bash
flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons:main -f flutter_launcher_icons_partner.yaml
flutter build ios --release -t lib/main_partner.dart --build-name=1.0.1 --build-number=2
# Bundle ID in Xcode: com.example.playmakeradmin (for updating existing app)
```

