## ЁЯЧДя╕П Database (Supabase)

**Key Tables:**
- `player_profiles` / `users` тЖТ User accounts
- `football_fields` тЖТ Field data
  - `username` тЖТ Field owner email (for PARTNER login)
  - `password` тЖТ Field owner password (for PARTNER login)
  - `availableTimeSlots` тЖТ Timeslots data
- `bookings` тЖТ Booking records
  - `footballFieldId` тЖТ Links to field
  - `price` тЖТ Revenue tracking

