## ЁЯЪл Git Rules - NEVER COMMIT THESE FILES

When making commits, NEVER stage or commit:

### Build Artifacts
- `**/build/` - Any build folder
- `promoapp/build/` - Promo app build outputs
- `*.aab`, `*.apk`, `*.ipa` - Binary files

### Screenshots & Media at Root
- `/*.png` - Screenshots at project root
- `/*.jpg`, `/*.jpeg`, `/*.gif` - Images at root
- `/*.mov`, `/*.mp4` - Videos at root
- `screen_*.png`, `emulator_*.png` - Emulator screenshots

### Generated Files
- `**/Generated.xcconfig` - Flutter iOS generated config
- `**/flutter_export_environment.sh` - Flutter generated
- `fastlane/report.xml` - Fastlane output
- `fastlane/README.md` - Auto-generated

### Credentials (SECURITY!)
- `*.p8` - App Store Connect API keys
- `*-service-account.json` - Google Play credentials
- `.env` files

### Large Folders
- `node_modules/`
- `**/Pods/`
- `**/.gradle/`
- `albaseet-website/`

**Before committing, always check `git status` and ensure no build artifacts or screenshots are staged!**

